==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Blushless
<hw>Blush"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Free from blushes; incapable of
blushing; shameless; impudent.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Vice now, secure, her <qex>blushless</qex> front shall raise.</q>
<rj><qau>Dodsley.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Blushy</ent>⟦br⟧
